90
00:10:16,667 --> 00:10:19,066
I sto biste na prvi pogled
mogli da me...

91
00:10:19,067 --> 00:10:22,665
Pacov u mojoj supi!
I ja je pojedoh!

92
00:10:25,438 --> 00:10:27,033
U pravu je!
To je pacov!

93
00:10:27,034 --> 00:10:30,142
Polim lepo.
To je pacov!

94
00:10:30,143 --> 00:10:33,043
Dovedite mi tog pacova!

95
00:10:33,044 --> 00:10:35,093
Molim Vas, nemojte
donositi ishitrene zakljucke.

96
00:10:35,094 --> 00:10:39,011
I razumem da imate na umu sta
sa ovim pacovom,

97
00:10:39,012 --> 00:10:41,309
Ipak ja...

98
00:10:41,310 --> 00:10:44,455
...nisam odavde, ja sam iz...

99
00:10:45,149 --> 00:10:47,362
Mnogo ste nervozni.

100
