Onde, ispod!

103
00:11:00,962 --> 00:11:04,985
Zaustavite tog pacova!

104
00:11:05,508 --> 00:11:07,606
Uhvatite ga!
Eno ga ispod!

105
00:11:14,587 --> 00:11:17,644
Ide blizu supe!

106
00:11:19,844 --> 00:11:21,143
Eno ga!!

107
00:11:21,144 --> 00:11:22,944
Izvinite, molim vas,
ja jednostavno..

108
00:11:30,158 --> 00:11:32,391
Onde, ispod.

109
00:11:40,935 --> 00:11:50,699
Slatka moja...
je...

110
00:11:50,700 --> 00:11:54,819
Mrtav je!
Uhvatite ga!

111
